OL,3,CZoo staff say public have reported
OL,4,C'several sightings' of missing
OL,5,Ccapybara Samba
OL,7,FThermal drones and camera traps are
OL,8,Fbeing used in regular searches and
OL,9,Fteams say they have carefully
OL,10,Finvestigated each report, but believe
OL,11,Fthat some reported sightings were
OL,12,Fmuntjac deer.
OL,14,FThe park added that Tango, Samba's
OL,15,Fsister continues to do well and
OL,16,Fremains in her private habitat while
OL,17,Fwork is completed on her new home at
OL,18,Fthe front of the park.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
