PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1778249473
OL,3,CZoo staff say public have reported
OL,4,C'several sightings' of missing
OL,5,Ccapybara Samba
OL,7,F"On the evening of Wednesday 6th May,
OL,8,Fwe received a report of a possible
OL,9,Fsighting of Samba along Highbridge
OL,10,FRoad.
OL,12,F"Our team headed out to the area
OL,13,Fshortly afterwards, however there was
OL,14,Funfortunately no sign of her. A camera
OL,15,Ftrap has now been installed in the
OL,16,Farea to help monitor any further
OL,17,Factivity."
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
